<h4>collect : Creates a new array containing the values returned by the block.</h4>
<p>array = (1..10).to_a<p>
<%= array = (1..10).to_a %><br>

<p>array.collect{ |num| num * num }<p>
<%= array.collect{ |num| num * num } %><br>

<h4>select : Elements can be selected from an array according to criteria defined in a block.</h4>

<p>array.select{ |num| num < 5 }<p>
<%= array.select{ |num| num < 5 } %><br>

<p>array.select{ |num| num.even? }<p>
<%= array.select{ |num| num.even? } %><br>

