<h4>Use Symbol to_proc</h4>

<%= 'The & calls to_proc on the object, and passes it as a block to the method. The following calls are equivalent:' %><br>
<br>
<b><%= '%w(jonh mary michael).map { |x| x.upcase }' %></b><br>
<%= %w(jonh mary michael).map { |x| x.upcase } %><br>

<br>
<b><%= '%w(jonh mary michael).map(&:upcase)' %></b><br>
<%= %w(jonh mary michael).map(&:upcase) %><br>